title: piratebaybootscreen.zip
description:
This archive contains 3 files.


thepiratebaybootscreen.bootscreen - A bootscreen format used for StyleXP application. See www.stardock.net for how to use StyleXP.

thepiratebaybootscreen.png - The flat PNG image in a lossless format.

thepiratebaybootscreen.xcf- The lossless gimp file that includes layer info so you can edit in gimp and alter the colours if you wish. See www.gimp.org for the free app.

Just a little something I rustled up today as I was off sick and bored, and I'm learning to use Gimp!

- Dac 

(aka Wakizashimaster)
